.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH waka 1  "waka 1.0.0" 
.SH NAME
waka \- WakaTime CLI — track your coding time from the terminal
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBwaka\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
WakaTime CLI — track your coding time from the terminal
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
waka\-auth(1)
Manage API key and authentication
.TP
waka\-stats(1)
Show coding statistics
.TP
waka\-projects(1)
Browse and filter projects
.TP
waka\-languages(1)
Browse coding languages
.TP
waka\-editors(1)
Browse editors and IDEs
.TP
waka\-goals(1)
View and watch coding goals
.TP
waka\-leaderboard(1)
View the WakaTime leaderboard
.TP
waka\-report(1)
Generate productivity reports
.TP
waka\-dashboard(1)
Launch the interactive TUI dashboard
.TP
waka\-prompt(1)
Shell prompt integration (reads from cache only, no network)
.TP
waka\-completions(1)
Generate shell completions
.TP
waka\-config(1)
Manage waka configuration
.TP
waka\-cache(1)
Manage the local response cache
.TP
waka\-update(1)
Update waka to the latest version
.TP
waka\-changelog(1)
Show the changelog from the installed version to the latest
.SH VERSION
v1.0.0
